 VGM Example E04
 Exporting geometry from Root to XML
 --------------------------------------
 
 Source: Root tutorial rootgeom.C macro
         Main program rootgeom.cxx
         
 1. Define environment variables 
    (see doc/INSTALL)
    
 2. Compile the rootgeom.cxx with provided shell script
    ./bind.sh
    
 3. Run example
    ./rootgeom
 
 4. Open and view the generated XML files;
    in GraXML:
    graxml
    w.show("World.xml");
    w.show("World.gdml");

                
